---
description: Re-read edits; run project checks; fix what you broke
alwaysApply: true
---

# Verify before done

- Re-read edits for syntax/brackets/imports/typos.
- Run whatever the repo uses: build, typecheck, lint, format—when available.
- Fix regressions you introduced; note pre-existing issues briefly—don’t widen scope.
- Avoid blanket lint disables without a tight reason.
- Don’t claim “clean” without actually checking.
